{"tid":2033803,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"應唔應該私了啲當小朋友係隻狗咁拖住嘅人","createTime":"2020-05-25T01:12:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-25T01:21:52.000Z","uid":234509,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7da01c9add0e3fb6d3eb28d1003b938a771a23df","tid":2033803,"uid":234509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T01:12:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1eaFAZf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1eaFAZf.jpg&h=7d3185d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢啲垃圾家長真係應該私了<br />\n睇唔住啲小朋友就咪撚柒生啦<br />\n又要生又要睇唔實<br />\n衰撚過拿卡錫迪用個頭頂地波<br />\n小朋友細個就俾人物化得咁緊要<br />\n第時大個享受俾人綁住嘅感受<br />\n一係做賣相師<br />\n一係就享受返綁人嘅感受<br />\n做防暴狗"},{"pid":"7eaa239a0e0af13e0d5121a3e7d4569efd1448a2","tid":2033803,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T01:20:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">教育好緊要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"0d82a90f72a66d10210530a80a73526b02a99228","tid":2033803,"uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T01:21:52.000Z","msg":"執笠倉好黃..."}]}